      <title>盈利季面临重大考验：零售商的节日前景</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/earnings-season-faces-major-test-retailers-holiday-outlooks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[上周的抛售就发生在美国企业普遍成功的财报季之后，投资者正准备迎接最后一个考验：未来几天将公布的一系列零售业领头羊的零售业报告，以了解消费者的消费状况。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/earnings-season-faces-major-test-retailers-holiday-outlooks</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Nov 2024 10:00:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
